* Implements a repository layer for the API
* The layer is constructed in [index.ts](mdc:apps/api/src/internal/storage/index.ts)
* Exports sub-repository (i.e. `ProjectRepository`) interfaces in [index.ts](mdc:apps/api/src/internal/storage/interfaces/index.ts)
    * Rules for writing interfaces in [interfaces.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/api/storage/interfaces.mdc)   
* Exports implementations of the repository interfaces in [index.ts](mdc:apps/api/src/internal/storage/implementaions/index.ts)
    * Rules for implementing interfaces in [implementations.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/api/storage/implementations.mdc)
* Use Dizzle ORM for the implementations, via a package in [client.ts](mdc:packages/db/src/client.ts)
* One repository per domain.
